					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Anes wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">its working but i use precalculated AT BYTE location and SHR amount.</div>
<br />Define "precalculated". The real PPU 'calculates' the attribute byte address/shift based on the nametable address it fetched from immediately prior.
<br />(when I say 'calculates' I mean 'takes certain groups of bits from the VRAM address and rearranges them')</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
